reactor.rx

Class BiStreams

  • java.lang.Object
    • reactor.rx.Streams
      • reactor.rx.BiStreams

  • public class BiStreams
extends Streams
    A Streams add-on to work with key/value pairs hydrated in Tuple2. Main factories support binding incoming values into arbitrary Map stores by key.
    Author:
    Stephane Maldini
